description:
Kendall is a hot-n-spicey latin homeboy.
He likes to party, socialize, and make the scene. The dude has got acting as well as voice over or tv host in his future. This guy is smooth!
Speaking of smooth, he is naturally smooth, but had been growing out his beard a bit for his Halloween costume. I love how masculine he looks all stubbly like.
Kendall is very competitive too. Name a sport and he likely excels at it. He's nursing some pretty good scrapes here and there, received in a flag football game that got out of hand. He surfs every other day, hence the body suit tanlines.
He totally got into being filmed, and the more we shot the more turned on he got.
Enjoy!
title: Kendall - Solo
